In this review study, species Use Values (UV s) and family Use Values (UV f) were employed by modifying the equation for UV is, as proposed by Tardío and Pardo-de-Santayana [ 21]:
\documentclass[12pt]{minimal} \usepackage{amsmath} \usepackage{wasysym} \usepackage{amsfonts} \usepackage{amssymb} \usepackage{amsbsy} \usepackage{mathrsfs} \usepackage{upgreek} \setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt} \begin{document}$$ \mathrm{U}\mathrm{V}s=\sum \mathrm{U}s/\mathrm{N}s $$\end{document}
UV s = ∑ U s / N s
